Joe Rickson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joe_Rickson 0 Joe Rickson (born Oscar Erickson, September 6, 1880 – January 8, 1958) was an American actor of the silent era. He appeared in 90 films between 1913 and 1945. He was born in Clearcreek, Montana and died in Los Angeles, California.
